## 2. THE ANXIETY ISOLATION ENGINE (INPUT VS. OUTPUT MATRIX)
To maintain mental stamina and prevent panic-driven decision-making, decouple daily operational evaluation from external market chaos.

| Metric Type | Definition / Boundary | Examples (100% Controlled) | System Action |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Input Metrics** | Actions under your absolute, direct logical control. | Sending 3 custom pitches weekly; publishing 1 case study. | **Track & Enforce:** If inputs are met, system status is **GREEN**, regardless of revenue noise. |
| **Output Metrics** | Results influenced by external human or market variables. | Total monthly revenue; client response speed. | **Observe Only:** Use purely as trailing data to adjust input strategy, never as a daily emotional driver. |

